# TIME command tests - Get server time
@name TIME
@group server
@since 2.6.0

=== TEST: TIME returns array
RUN:
TIME
EXPECT:
(any)

=== TEST: TIME returns seconds and microseconds
RUN:
TIME
EXPECT:
(any)

=== TEST: TIME positive values
RUN:
TIME
EXPECT:
(any)

=== TEST: TIME format
RUN:
TIME
EXPECT:
(any)

=== TEST: TIME wrong number of arguments
RUN:
TIME extra
EXPECT:
(error) ERR wrong number of arguments for 'time' command
